---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import LegacyHeader from '../components/LegacyHeader.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import ContactSection from '../components/ContactSection.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import ButtonPrimary from '../components/ButtonPrimary.astro';
import ButtonSecondary from '../components/ButtonSecondary.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="SEO Services Philippines | Bright Forge SEO"
  description="Bright Forge delivers transparent SEO services for Philippine businesses that need stronger rankings, better leads and clearer commercial growth."
  faqs={[
    { question: "What SEO services do Philippine businesses usually need first?", answer: "Most campaigns start with technical SEO, keyword mapping, on-page improvements, internal linking and content gap work. Local businesses also need Google Business Profile optimisation and location signals, while national or ecommerce sites usually need stronger architecture, category content and authority building." },
    { question: "How long does SEO take to work?", answer: "Technical fixes and on-page improvements can show movement within weeks, but meaningful commercial growth usually takes 3 to 6 months. Competitive markets often need 6 to 12 months of consistent technical, content and authority work." },
    { question: "Do we still need SEO if AI search is changing Google?", answer: "Yes. AI search still depends on clear, crawlable, trustworthy source material. We treat AI readiness as a layer on top of SEO, not a replacement for technical health, strong content, links, reviews and conversion-focused pages." },
    { question: "What makes Bright Forge different from cheap SEO packages?", answer: "We do not sell mystery tasks or thin monthly busywork. We prioritise the fixes that can affect rankings, leads and revenue, then show what changed, what the data says and what should happen next." }
  ]}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json">
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
        "itemListElement": [
          {
            "@type": "ListItem",
            "position": 1,
            "name": "Home",
            "item": "https://brightforge.com.ph/"
          },
          {
            "@type": "ListItem",
            "position": 2,
            "name": "SEO Services Philippines",
            "item": "https://brightforge.com.ph/seo-services-philippines/"
          }
        ]
      }
    </script>
    <script type="application/ld+json">
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "WebPage",
        "name": "SEO Services Philippines | Bright Forge SEO",
        "url": "https://brightforge.com.ph/seo-services-philippines/",
        "inLanguage": "en",
        "description": "Transparent, results-focused SEO services in the Philippines. We combine technical excellence, strategic content, and ethical link building to drive rankings, traffic, and revenue.",
        "publisher": {
          "@type": "Organization",
          "name": "Bright Forge SEO",
          "url": "https://brightforge.com.ph/"
        },
        "mainEntity": {
          "@type": "ItemList",
          "itemListOrder": "http://schema.org/ItemListOrderAscending",
          "itemListElement": [
            {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Technical SEO", "url": "https://brightforge.com.ph/technical-seo-services-philippines/"},
            {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "On-Page SEO", "url": "https://brightforge.com.ph/on-page-seo-services-philippines/"},
            {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Content SEO", "url": "https://brightforge.com.ph/content-seo-services-philippines/"},
            {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 4, "name": "Local SEO", "url": "https://brightforge.com.ph/local-seo-services-philippines/"},
            {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 5, "name": "SEO Audits", "url": "https://brightforge.com.ph/seo-audit-services/"},
            {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 6, "name": "Keyword Research", "url": "https://brightforge.com.ph/keyword-research-services/"},
            {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 7, "name": "Link Building", "url": "https://brightforge.com.ph/backlink-seo-services-philippines/"},
            {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 8, "name": "AI Search Optimization", "url": "https://brightforge.com.ph/ai-search-optimization-services-philippines/"},
            {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 9, "name": "Astro Website Development", "url": "https://brightforge.com.ph/development/astro/"},
            {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 10, "name": "Website Migration", "url": "https://brightforge.com.ph/website-migration-services/"},
            {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 11, "name": "White Label SEO", "url": "https://brightforge.com.ph/white-label-seo-services-philippines/"}
          ]
        }
      }
    </script>
  </Fragment>
  <LegacyHeader slot="header" />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <Hero
    badgeIcon="fas fa-chart-line"
    badgeText="Complete SEO Solutions"
    title="SEO Services <span>Philippines</span>"
    breadcrumbCurrent="SEO Services Philippines"
  >
    <Fragment slot="story">
      <p>SEO is not a bundle of disconnected tasks. We fix the parts of the site that stop search engines understanding it, strengthen the pages that should win enquiries, and build the trust signals needed to compete in tougher Philippine and international markets.</p>
      <p>That means technical clean-up, content that matches buyer intent, internal links that guide authority, and reporting that connects movement in rankings to leads, sales and pipeline. AI search readiness sits on top of that foundation, because Google and AI tools both need clear, reliable source material before they can recommend a business.</p>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="actions">
      <ButtonPrimary href="/contact/" text="Get Started" />
      <ButtonSecondary href="#services" text="Explore Services" />
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="stats">
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">1000+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Websites Ranked</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">15+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Years Experience</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">98%</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Client Retention</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <!-- Services Overview -->
  <section id="services" class="services-overview">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">Our Expertise</div>
        <h2>Fully-Managed <span>SEO Services</span></h2>
        <p>Everything you need to improve technical health, build topical authority, and earn trust with search engines and users.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="services-grid">
        <!-- Core SEO -->
        <a class="service-card" href="/technical-seo-services-philippines/">
          <div class="service-card-inner">
            <h3>Technical SEO</h3>
            <p>Fix crawl, indexation, Core Web Vitals, and site architecture issues that hold rankings back.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a class="service-card" href="/on-page-seo-services-philippines/">
          <div class="service-card-inner">
            <h3>On-Page SEO</h3>
            <p>Optimize titles, headings, internal links, and page experience to lift relevance and engagement.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a class="service-card" href="/content-seo-services-philippines/">
          <div class="service-card-inner">
            <h3>Content SEO</h3>
            <p>Research-driven content planning and optimization that builds topical authority and conversions.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a class="service-card" href="/local-seo-services-philippines/">
          <div class="service-card-inner">
            <h3>Local SEO</h3>
            <p>Improve visibility in maps and local organic results with Google Business Profile optimisation, citations, location content and review signals.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Strategy & Growth -->
        <a class="service-card" href="/seo-audit-services/">
          <div class="service-card-inner">
            <h3>SEO Audits</h3>
            <p>Clear, prioritized action plans that diagnose technical, content, and authority gaps.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a class="service-card" href="/keyword-research-services/">
          <div class="service-card-inner">
            <h3>Keyword Research</h3>
            <p>Intent-led keyword mapping to guide pages, internal links, and content calendars.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a class="service-card" href="/backlink-seo-services-philippines/">
          <div class="service-card-inner">
            <h3>Link Building</h3>
            <p>Quality-first outreach and digital PR to earn links that move rankings safely.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a class="service-card" href="/ai-search-optimization-services-philippines/">
          <div class="service-card-inner">
            <h3>AI Search Optimization</h3>
            <p>Make your SEO foundations easier for Google, AI answers and agentic search tools to understand, cite and recommend.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Development & Partnerships -->
        <a class="service-card" href="/development/astro/">
          <div class="service-card-inner">
            <h3>Astro Website Development</h3>
            <p>Lightning-fast, SEO-first sites built on Astro with best-in-class page experience.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a class="service-card" href="/website-migration-services/">
          <div class="service-card-inner">
            <h3>Website Migration</h3>
            <p>Protect hard-earned rankings during redesigns, replatforming, and domain changes.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a class="service-card" href="/white-label-seo-services-philippines/">
          <div class="service-card-inner">
            <h3>White Label SEO</h3>
            <p>Reliable fulfillment partner for agencies needing expert SEO delivery under your brand.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="why-us">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">Why Bright Forge</div>
        <h2>Performance-Driven <span>SEO Excellence</span></h2>
        <p>We combine technical diagnosis, practical implementation and commercial judgement. The goal is not to make reports look busy. It is to move the pages that can win qualified traffic and turn that traffic into enquiries.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Data-Driven Strategies</h3>
          <p>Every recommendation is tied to evidence: crawl data, search demand, competitor gaps, analytics and the commercial value of the page.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>White-Hat Excellence</h3>
          <p>Sustainable growth through ethical SEO practices that build long-term authority and protect your brand reputation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Rapid Implementation</h3>
          <p>Quick turnaround on critical fixes and optimizations with clear priorities and measurable impact tracking.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Expert Team</h3>
          <p>Senior SEO specialists with 15+ years combined experience delivering results for global brands and local businesses.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="seo-faq-section">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge">SEO Questions</div>
        <h2>What businesses usually ask before starting SEO</h2>
        <p>Clear answers before the proposal stage, because good SEO should not feel like buying fog in a jar.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="seo-faq-list">
        <article class="seo-faq-item">
          <h3>What SEO services do Philippine businesses usually need first?</h3>
          <p>Most campaigns start with technical SEO, keyword mapping, on-page improvements, internal linking and content gap work. Local businesses also need Google Business Profile optimisation and location signals, while national or ecommerce sites usually need stronger architecture, category content and authority building.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="seo-faq-item">
          <h3>How long does SEO take to work?</h3>
          <p>Technical fixes and on-page improvements can show movement within weeks, but meaningful commercial growth usually takes 3 to 6 months. Competitive markets often need 6 to 12 months of consistent technical, content and authority work.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="seo-faq-item">
          <h3>Do we still need SEO if AI search is changing Google?</h3>
          <p>Yes. AI search still depends on clear, crawlable, trustworthy source material. We treat AI readiness as a layer on top of SEO, not a replacement for technical health, strong content, links, reviews and conversion-focused pages.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="seo-faq-item">
          <h3>What makes Bright Forge different from cheap SEO packages?</h3>
          <p>We do not sell mystery tasks or thin monthly busywork. We prioritise the fixes that can affect rankings, leads and revenue, then show what changed, what the data says and what should happen next.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-final">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2>Ready to Grow with <span>SEO</span>?</h2>
      <p>Tell us about your goals and we’ll recommend the right mix of audits, content, and optimization to get you there.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
        <ButtonPrimary href="/contact/" text="Request a Free Consultation" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ContactSection id="contact" />
  <Footer slot="footer" />
</MainLayout>

<style>
/********************
  CSS Variables
*********************/
:root {
  --brand-accent: #f0622a;
  --brand-dark: #e8eaf2;
  --brand-soft: #7a7f99;
  --brand-light: #0d0f1a;
  --gradient-primary: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0622a 0%, #d4510e 100%);
  --gradient-secondary: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4510e 0%, #f0622a 100%);
  --shadow-soft: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  --shadow-medium: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
}

/********************
  Hero Stats (for stats slot)
*********************/
.hero-stats {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 2rem;
  padding: 2rem;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border-radius: 16px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
}

.stat {
  text-align: center;
}

.stat-number {
  display: block;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: white !important;
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.stat-label {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) !important;
}

/********************
  Services Overview
*********************/
.services-overview {
  background: var(--brand-light);
  padding: 5rem 0;
}

.services-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 2rem;
}

.service-card {
  position: relative;
  display: block;
  text-decoration: none;
  background: #131627;
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 2rem;
  border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.service-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 4px;
  background: var(--gradient-secondary);
}

.service-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);
}

.service-card h3 {
  color: var(--brand-text, #e8eaf2);
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.service-card p {
  color: #ffffff;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/********************
  Why Choose Us
*********************/
.why-us {
  background: #131627;
  padding: 5rem 0;
}

.benefits-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
  gap: 2rem;
}

.benefit-card {
  position: relative;
  background: #131627;
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 2rem;
  text-align: center;
  border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.benefit-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 4px;
  background: var(--gradient-secondary);
}

.benefit-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);
}

.benefit-icon {
  width: 70px;
  height: 70px;
  margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
  background: var(--gradient-primary);
  border-radius: 16px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 1.75rem;
  color: white;
}

.benefit-card h3 {
  color: var(--brand-text, #e8eaf2);
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.benefit-card p {
  color: #ffffff;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.seo-faq-section {
  padding: 5rem 0;
  background: #131627;
}

.seo-faq-list {
  display: grid;
  gap: 1rem;
}

.seo-faq-item {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  border-radius: 1rem;
  padding: 1.5rem;
}

.seo-faq-item h3 {
  color: #e8eaf2;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  margin-bottom: .75rem;
}

.seo-faq-item p {
  color: #d0d4e8;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

/********************
  Final CTA
*********************/
.cta-final {
  background: var(--brand-light);
  padding: 5rem 0;
}

.cta-final h2 {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3rem);
  font-weight: 900;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  color: var(--brand-text, #e8eaf2);
}

.cta-final h2 span {
  color: #f0622a;
}

.cta-final p {
  color: #ffffff;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.section-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.section-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 8px 16px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(240, 98, 42, 0.1) 0%, rgba(240, 98, 42, 0.05) 100%);
  border: 1px solid rgba(240, 98, 42, 0.15);
  color: #f0622a;
  border-radius: 100px;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.section-header h2 {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  color: var(--brand-text, #e8eaf2);
}

.section-header h2 span {
  color: #f0622a;
}

.section-header p {
  color: #ffffff;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/********************
  Responsive
*********************/
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero-stats {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .services-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .benefits-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}
</style>
